Package it.polimi.ingsw.model.playerclasses

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AmmoPocket
    This class represents the ammo available to the player
    DamageTrack
    This class represents the damage of the player
    DoubleKillCounter
    This class contains the list of the players who made double kills during the game, and the value of the double kills
    KillshotTrack
    This class contains the killshot track, and throws exceptions to signal when the frenzy mod must start
    MarkTrack
    This class represents the marks of the player
    MarkTrackMapKeyDeserializer
    This class is used to deserialize a MarkTrack object from a JSON file.
    Player
    This class all the elements necessary to a player to play a match.
    PointTrack
    This class contains the points for damage of the player
    PowerupPocket
    This class represents the set of the powerups available to the player
    StartingPlayerMarker
    This class marks the player who started the game, which is needed in the final frenzy phase
    WeaponPocket
    This class represents the set of the weapons available to the player
